  "text": "allows us to estimate the kinematic viscosity\u03bd BH \u223c M , which is related to the shear viscosity by\u03b7 BH = \u03c1 BH\u03bdBH and to the bulk viscosity by\u03b6 BH = \u2212\u03b7 BH [CITATION_1] . Estimating the BH density as \u03c1 BH \u223c M/[(4\u03c0/3)R ",
